    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 📤Email Outreach Executor\n\n**Purpose**\nAutomatically sends personalized cold emails to leads that are fully enriched and ready for outreach. Uses Gmail to send.\n\n**How it works**\nRuns every **hour** → picks top 10 highest-scoring leads → checks unsubscribe list → builds personalized email from AI-generated content → sends via Gmail → logs activity → marks lead as contacted.\n\n**Key Rules**\n- Only sends to leads at `enrichment_stage = 3`\n- **Unsubscribed emails are never contacted**\n- After sending, sets `outreach_status = email_sent`\n- Includes unsubscribe instructions in every email",
